Title: 15 Minutes With
Tagline: Meet Cheyenne, Berlin model and It Girl
ChatText: we met cheyenne in berin for a chat
IntroText: Berlin It Girl and model Cheyenne Tulsa has a special love for Chinese food, coffee and art. From Australia but currently living in Berlin, Cheyenne inspires us with her impeccable taste for fashion and interior design and gives us a daily glimpse into her life in Berlin.

LeftQuestion.question: What does time mean to you?
LeftQuestion.answer: That time shouldn’t go to waste

LeftQuestion.question: Latest discovery?
LeftQuestion.answer: Ming's Garden in Kudamm… seriously the best chinese food I’ve had in Berlin.

LeftQuestion.question: What is your morning routine?
LeftQuestion.answer: The first thing I do is make a coffee... or two. Afterwards I spend time replying back and forth to emails, then I have a shower, get dressed and start my day.

RightQuestion.question: Favorite spot in Berlin?
RightQuestion.answer: I live in Kreuzberg so I'm surrounded by so many of my favourite places. In the Summer I love to hang by the canal or in the park with friends. Jungbusch and Lugosi for drinks. Coffee from Carpenter coffee is the best, Zola's for pizza, Mugrabi or Stella's i for lunch, Eggs Benedict at Le Bon, Hangover cure at Cabslam, the list goes on...

RightQuestion.question: Who or what is the essence of beauty for you?
RightQuestion.answer: Someone who has the confidence to celebrate their imperfections.

RightQuestion.question: On Sundays I…
RightQuestion.answer: Am checking out an exhibition somewhere, with my friends, doing sport, chilling in bed...

Name: Cheyenne

CenterQuestion.question: what do you like most about your day off?
CenterQuestion.answer: It’s very rare for me to have a day off but if I do I usually visit an area or store I’ve wanted to go to, or I develop ideas and projects that are on my list of things to do.

LeftQuestion.question: What is your best memory?
LeftQuestion.answer: The day I moved from Australia to Europe.

RightQuestion.question: Who or what inspired you in life and why?
RightQuestion.answer: My mom. She’s the most inspiring, warm hearted, hardest working woman I know.

WatchSection.WatchText: The Tribeca in white - gold, shiny but classy.

LeftQuestion.question: One thing that most people do not know about you?
LeftQuestion.answer: I like K-pop and I play the electric bass guitar.

LeftQuestion.question: I'm always late / punctual. How so?
LeftQuestion.answer: No matter what, I always try to be on time.

LeftQuestion.question: In five years time I…
LeftQuestion.answer: Evolve my new project (launching very soon). Keep traveling, own an apartment by the ocean somewhere and keep tricking things off my 'to do' list.

RightQuestion.question: Where would you be instantly on the spot, if you could?
RightQuestion.answer: Somewhere tropical by the ocean sipping from a coconut under the sun my bikini on, surrounded by seafood and acai bowls

RightQuestion.question: Gold or silver?
RightQuestion.answer: Both, but I have a rule I never mix gold and silver together.

MainCloseImageText.QuoteText: My best memory is the day I moved from Australia to Europe.
